<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link260208" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=260208&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F240008-is-it-necessary-to-read-all-five-books-of%2Fanswers%2F260208-it-is-absolutely">flag</a>
