          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/426944.T_H_White"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1246071532p3/426944.jpg);'></div>
